org.safs.tools

Class CaseInsensitiveFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.safs.tools.CaseInsensitiveFile

  • public class CaseInsensitiveFile
extends java.lang.Object
    This Class is meant to extend File behavior allowing for case insensitive files. This "has a" internal protected File object and all File methods are implemented by simplying returning the internal File.method() for all File methods. The toFile() method returns the internal File object.

    This class has no SAFS dependencies and can be packaged independent of other SAFS classes.

    Author:
    Jack Imbriani
